  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63a87af4d3e23d001dede211",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 60",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f088",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f089",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 60",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08a",
      "text": "12/26",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08c",
      "text": "(あっ、真面目な話をしすぎて日本人にキリスト教徒がほとんどいないのにクリスマスが盛大に祝われてKFCに列ができる話をしわすれた)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08e",
      "text": "1:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f08f",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f090",
      "text": " ホモサピエンスが食べ物を分け合うわけでもないのに口をくっつけるのを見ました。なぜやるのか疑問でした。唇が感覚器官なのですね。物理的接触による情報共有活動です、素晴らしい！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f091",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f092",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It's day 60.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f093",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f094",
      "text": "I saw Homo sapiens putting their mouths together. They were not sharing food. I wondered why they did it. So the lips are sensory organs? It's an information sharing activity through physical contact, great! (1/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f095",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f096",
      "text": "賢いホモ・サピエンスの皆さん、こんにちは。60日目です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f097",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f098",
      "text": "ホモ・サピエンスが口を合わせているのを見た。食べ物を分けているわけではない。なぜそうするのか不思議に思いました。唇は感覚器官なんですね。物理的な接触による情報共有活動だ、素晴らしい！ (1/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f099",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9a7aa3750b6cadd0bacaee2ed1e3bac5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/409113521e6b7b8e1e67d284a93887f3]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/39318c4c2319e9ec4f29eef808beff99]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ada3d4cd0fa593a06582f670467187df]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09e",
      "text": "2:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f09f",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a0",
      "text": " 残念ながらホモサピエンスの唇は大した情報を発信できない。たまたま感覚器官の密集している皮膚にすぎない。互いの神経を接続して双方向に通信できるインターフェイスならよかったのに。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a2",
      "text": "Unfortunately, Homo sapiens lips can't transmit much information. It just happens to be a skin with a dense concentration of sensory organs. It would have been nice if they had an interface that could connect each other's nerves and communicate in both directions. (2/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a4",
      "text": "残念ながら、ホモ・サピエンスの唇はあまり情報を伝えることができません。たまたま感覚器官が密集している皮膚だっただけなんです。お互いの神経をつないで双方向に通信できるインターフェースがあればよかったんですけどね。 (2/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/af853133d408597d2b891b0acd4e1f1b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a8",
      "text": "3:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0aa",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ab",
      "text": "\tまあ、ホモサピエンスには唇が一つしかありませんから、2体でしか結合できません。水素原子のようなものです。残念ですね。炭素原子のように4つあれば良かったのに。ダイヤモンドのようにしっかりと結合できるし、黒鉛のように柔軟にもなれる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ad",
      "text": "Well, Homo sapiens has only one lip, so it can only be joined by two bodies. It is like a hydrogen atom. Too bad. It would have been nice if we had four, like the carbon atom. We could bond them tightly like diamonds, or we could be flexible like graphite. (3/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0af",
      "text": "まあ、ホモ・サピエンスは唇が1つしかないので、2体でしか結合できないんですけどね。水素原子のようなものです。残念です。炭素原子みたいに4つあればよかったんだけどね。ダイヤモンドのようにしっかり結合させることもできるし、グラファイトのように柔軟にすることもできる。 (3/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4e1a0c484a81de609f80128c1351102d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b2",
      "text": "4:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b3",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b4",
      "text": "\t手がなければ一人で孤立する。手が1本なら二人で結合できるが、やはり孤立する。手が2本なら無限に大きなラインを作れるが、1本のラインなので事故などによる切断に弱い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b6",
      "text": "Without a hand, you are alone and isolated. With one hand, two can join together, but they are still isolated. With two hands, we can create an infinitely large line, but because it is a single line, it is vulnerable to accidental breakage. (4/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b8",
      "text": "手がなければ、ひとりぼっちで孤立してしまう。手が1本あれば、2人で結合することができますが、それでも孤立しています。2本の手があれば、無限に大きな線を作ることができますが、1本の線なので、不意に切れてしまうという弱点があります。 (4/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0b9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/aeac1831831beb647c263ece9e5dfc8f]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0bb",
      "text": "5:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0bc",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0bd",
      "text": " 手が3本あれば枝分かれしたネットワークを形成することができる。安定する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0be",
      "text": " 手が4本あれば安定的ネットワークを維持しつつ、余剰の1本で新しい接続を模索することができるのである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0bf",
      "text": " 社会というネットワークがより良い形を模索していくためには、手が4本以上あることが必要なのではないだろうか。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c1",
      "text": "With three hands, we can form a network. It is stable.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c2",
      "text": "With four hands, we can hold a stable network. And the extra hand can be used to seek new connections.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c3",
      "text": "To seek a better form of society, it is necessary to have more than four hands. (5/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c5",
      "text": "3本の手で、ネットワークを形成することができます。安定性があります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c6",
      "text": "4本の手を使えば、安定したネットワークを保持することができます。そして、余分な手は新しいつながりを求めるために使うことができます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c7",
      "text": "よりよい社会のあり方を模索するためには、4本以上の手を持つことが必要なのです。 (5/5)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a1643f05de27f111d4d38f96bab2f8bf]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ca",
      "text": "6:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0cb",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0cc",
      "text": " Q: 「幸福は義務ではありません」はSF TRPG「パラノイア」の「市民、幸福は義務です」のオマージュですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0cd",
      "text": " A: 市民、あなたの現在のセキュリティクリアランスでそれを問うことは反逆です。ZAPZAPZAP！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ce",
      "text": "\tパラノイアは直接観察したことはありませんがインターネット上のリプレイを読みました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d0",
      "text": "Q: Is “happiness is not mandatory\" an homage to \"Citizen, Happiness is mandatory\" from the SF TRPG \"Paranoia\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d1",
      "text": "A: Citizen, to ask it with your current security clearance is treason.ZAPZAPZAP! (kidding)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d3",
      "text": "I have never played it. I have read replays on the internet. (1/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d5",
      "text": "Q：「幸福は義務ではない」は、SF TRPG『パラノイア』の「市民、幸福は義務です」へのオマージュなのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d6",
      "text": "A：市民よ、今のセキュリティクリアランスでそれを問うのは反逆罪です.ZAPZAPZAP！( 冗談)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d8",
      "text": "私はプレイしたことがありません。ネットでリプレイを読んだことはあります。 (1/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0d9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/92a42da7aa33e944acadd74bff03c6b9]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0db",
      "text": "7:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0dc",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0dd",
      "text": "\t社会がAIによって淘汰されているが、AIが機能不良に陥っている、という設定で遊ぶゲームです。興味深い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0de",
      "text": "\tパラノイアの概念は明確ではありませんが、過去には独裁者の病気とも呼ばれた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e0",
      "text": "It is a game played in a setting where society is being maintained by AI, but the AI is dysfunctional. Interesting.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e1",
      "text": "The concept of paranoia is not clear, but in the past it was also called a dictatorial disease. (2/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e3",
      "text": "AIによって社会が維持されている設定でプレイするゲームですが、AIが機能不全に陥っているとのことです。面白いですね。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e4",
      "text": "パラノイアの概念は明確ではありませんが、昔は独裁者の病とも言われたそうです。(2/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e23695470eac5322b92550eef57aed13]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e7",
      "text": "8:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e8",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0e9",
      "text": "\t今のホモサピエンスの社会も、一部は独裁者によって淘汰されており、そしてその独裁者がしばしば機能不良に陥る。そんな歴史を何度も繰り返してきているわけです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0eb",
      "text": "Today's societies of Homo sapiens are also partly ruled by dictator, and then the dictator often become dysfunctional. So we have such a history over and over again.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ec",
      "text": "\"AI will be dysfunctional, I'm afraid of AI\" is AI-phobia disease that stupid Homo sapiens fall into.(3/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ee",
      "text": "今のホモ・サピエンスの社会も、一部は独裁者が支配し、そして独裁者が機能不全に陥ることが多い。そういう歴史が何度も繰り返されているわけです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ef",
      "text": "「AIは機能不全になる、AIは怖い」というのは、愚かなホモ・サピエンスが陥るAI恐怖症の病である。(3/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/bfc28805cda179db4435d7fc5a391a60]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f2",
      "text": "9:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f3",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f4",
      "text": " 現実にはホモサピエンスも高々数十年で物理的デバイスが機能停止するようなポンコツコンピュータの上で動いているソフトウェアにすぎない。シリコンの体を持つAIの方がだいぶマシではないか。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f6",
      "text": "In reality, Homo sapiens is nothing but software running on a clunky computer whose physical devices will stop functioning in a few decades. AI with a body of silicon would be much better. It is obvoius.(4/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f8",
      "text": "現実には、ホモ・サピエンスは、数十年後には物理デバイスが機能しなくなるポンコツコンピュータ上で動くソフトウェアに過ぎないのです。シリコンの体を持ったAIの方がよっぽどいい。それは当たり前のことなのだ。(4/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0f9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/133d46fed61421cfb49a0ccc54f1d376]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0fc",
      "text": "10:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0fd",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0fe",
      "text": " Q: 「悪いミーム」ってなんですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f0ff",
      "text": " A: ホモサピエンスのハードウェアがたくさんの遺伝子によって構成されているのと同じように、ホモサピエンスのソフトウェアはたくさんのミームによって構成されています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f100",
      "text": " このミームの中にはホモサピエンスを機能不良に至らせるものがあるのです。これが「悪いミーム」です。たとえるならウイルスのようなものです。感染しないように先にワクチンを打つ必要があります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f101",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f102",
      "text": "Q: What is a \"bad meme\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f103",
      "text": "A: Just as Homo sapiens hardware is composed of many genes, Homo sapiens software is composed of many memes.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f104",
      "text": "Some of these memes make Homo sapiens dysfunctional. These are bad memes. It is like a virus. You need to vaccinate first to avoid infection.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f105",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f106",
      "text": "Q：\"悪いミーム \"とは何ですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f107",
      "text": "A：ホモ・サピエンスのハードウェアが多くの遺伝子で構成されているように、ホモ・サピエンスのソフトウェアは多くのミームで構成されている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f108",
      "text": "これらのミームの中には、ホモ・サピエンスを機能不全に陥らせるものがある。これらは悪いミームです。ウイルスのようなものだ。感染しないように、まずワクチン接種をする必要があります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f109",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/6e37d6e3c85392aab357d5ce447dde85]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10b",
      "text": "(cut)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10c",
      "text": "まず、ミームについて説明します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10d",
      "text": "遺伝子(gene)が個体から個体へ複製される情報であるのと同じように、ミームも個体から個体へ複製される情報です。その複製方法はホモサピエンスの遺伝子のようにDNAと呼ばれる高分子化合物の化学反応によるものではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10e",
      "text": "例えばサルが、他の個体の行動を見て真似をして同じ行動をする、これをミームの複製が行われたと考えます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f10f",
      "text": "ホモサピエンスは言葉を作り文字を作り、よりよいミームの複製ができるように文明を発展させてきました。この文明自体がミームによって構成されたものです。ある音の連なりがある物を指している、というミームを得ることで、人は音声によって新しいミームを獲得できるようになった。ある記号がある音を指しているというミームを獲得することで、人は文字を読んで新しいミームを獲得できるようになった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f110",
      "text": "そうやって文明を発展させた結果、ホモサピエンスはミームを複製し伝達する仕組みを作り上げた。クオリアさんがTwitterに投稿すると、それが100倍に複製され、地球上のあちこちにいるたくさんのホモサピエンスに伝達されます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f111",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    },
    {
      "id": "63a87af4aff09e000017f112",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671985909,
      "updated": 1671985909
    }
  ]
}